The books starts out with brief history of older movies from the early 1900s, but quickly moves into all the favorites we know. Star Trek, Star Wars, Gerry Anderson's series, Aliens, Battlestar Galactica, Babylon 5, and many others. No book can cover everything or every scifi movie and TV show ever made, but it does touch on the ones that were breakthroughs in how scifi was shown, and of course, the book is stocked full of color images of various space ships and gear.
